1
00:00:09,109 --> 00:00:11,178
DOCTOR: Amy? Amy? Whew..

2
00:00:11,311 --> 00:00:13,847
Amy, it's me, the Doctor.

3
00:00:14,047 --> 00:00:16,383
-Hello. Bit of a situation here.
-(ALARM BLARING)

4
00:00:16,483 --> 00:00:17,751
AUTOMATED VOICE: Intruder alert.

5
00:00:17,851 --> 00:00:20,153
I've got my finger on a button,
which is fine,

6
00:00:20,254 --> 00:00:21,922
but as soon as I
take my finger off the button,

7
00:00:22,022 --> 00:00:23,423
the spaceship is going to explode.

8
00:00:23,824 --> 00:00:25,259
(YELLING)

9
00:00:25,459 --> 00:00:27,194
Which is good in one way,

10
00:00:27,294 --> 00:00:29,496
because the spaceship in question
is about to attack the Earth,

11
00:00:29,596 --> 00:00:32,399
but bad in another way
because I'm on the spaceship

12
00:00:32,499 --> 00:00:35,302
and I'm going to get all smithereened.

13
00:00:35,402 --> 00:00:37,704
Now, plan.
I'm going to send you the coordinates

14
00:00:37,804 --> 00:00:39,506
so you can fly the Tardis here
and rescue me.

15
00:00:39,606 --> 00:00:42,009
Only three flaws in this plan,
far as I can see.

16
00:00:42,109 --> 00:00:43,911
One, I don't have the coordinates.

17
00:00:44,011 --> 00:00:45,412
Two, you can't fly the Tardis.

18
00:00:45,512 --> 00:00:48,815
Three... Oh, dear!
You're not even there.

19
00:00:48,916 --> 00:00:51,084
You left ages ago. Oh, well.

20
00:00:52,152 --> 00:00:54,621
I think I just wanted a chat
before all the...

21
00:00:55,822 --> 00:00:57,357
smithereening.

22
00:00:57,457 --> 00:00:59,693
(BEEPING RAPIDLY)

23
00:01:01,595 --> 00:01:03,530
(WHISPERING) Merry Christmas, Amelia.

24
00:01:03,897 --> 00:01:06,199
(HIGH-PITCHED TONE RINGING)

